4.00	Deserters	Desertion	In military terminology, desertion is the abandonment of a "duty" or post without permission and is done with the intention of not returning. "Absence Without Leave" (AWOL) can refer to either desertion or a temporary absence.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/15/Armenian_soldiers_with_deserters_cph.3c32320.jpg/220px-Armenian_soldiers_with_deserters_cph.3c32320.jpg
